*** Current Deploy recommentations

scp the deploy keys to the ~/.ssh directory

`git clone git@github.com:isotope11/hoplon-signaling-app.git`

Install node and nvm via this:
https://docs.aws.amazon.com/sdk-for-javascript/v2/developer-guide/setting-up-node-on-ec2-instance.html

`sudo apt-get update`
`sudo apt-get install build-essential`

Than you should be able to 

`node install`


